                <div class="slide">
                    <img src="/images/home/slide1.jpg" class="d-block w-100 h-100" alt="slide1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="title">
                            <h3>Welcome to Alexandria</h3>
                            <h5>What books will <em>you</em> discover?</h5>
                            <a asp-controller="Books"
                               asp-action="TopRated" class="btn">
                                search books
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <div class="slide">
                    <img src="/images/home//slide-5.jpg" class="d-block w-100" style="height: 731px;" alt="slide2">
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="title">
                            <h3>Welcome to Alexandria</h3>
                            <h5>What books will <em>you</em> discover?</h5>
                            <a asp-controller="Books"
                               asp-action="TopRated" class="btn">
                                search books
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <div class="slide">
                    <img src="/images/home/slide-6.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="slide1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="title">
                            <h3>Welcome to Alexandria</h3>
                            <h5>What books will <em>you</em> discover?</h5>
                            <a asp-controller="Books"
                               asp-action="TopRated" class="btn">
                                search books
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <div class="slide">
                    <img src="/images/home/slide-7.jpg" class="d-block w-100" style="height: 731px;" alt="slide1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="title">
                            <h3>Welcome to Alexandria</h3>
                            <h5>What books will <em>you</em> discover?</h5>
                            <a asp-controller="Books"
                               asp-action="TopRated" class="btn">
                                search books
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="recomended-sec">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
            <h2>Top 4 rated books</h2>
            <hr>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            @foreach (var book in Model.TopBooks)
            {
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="@book.PictureUrl" alt="Book Cover">
                        <h3>@book.Title</h3>
                        <h6><span><mark>@book.Genre</mark></span> / <mark>@book.Tag</mark></h6>
                        <div class="hover">
                            <a asp-controller="Books"
                               asp-action="Details"
                               asp-route-id="@book.Id">
                                <span><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="about-sec" id="about">
    <div class="about-img">
        <figure style="background:url(/images/about-img.jpg)no-repeat;"></figure>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Welcome to Alexandria</h2>
        <p>
            Our mission is to create a community, where anyone can discover new worlds, that may not even know existed, in the form of books. Here you will be able to see what your friends are reading, write reviews because half of the fun about reading is talking about what books make you think, feel and learn. You can chat with people all over the world and find best book for you. Whether you're looking for a textbook, a comic book, a romance, or a cookbook, the chances are very good that you'll find it here.
        </p>
        <p>
            Be part of our new world. Be inspired.
        </p>
        <div class="btn-sec">
            <a href="#" class="badge badge-warning">Search books</a>
            <a href="#" class="badge badge-warning">Write reviews</a>
            <a href="#" class="badge badge-warning">Chat with people</a>
            <a href="#" class="badge badge-warning">A lot of genres</a>
            <a href="#" class="badge badge-warning">A lot of tags</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-sm">
            <h5>Deciding what to read next?</h5>
            <p>You’re in the right place. Tell us what titles or genres you’ve enjoyed in the past, and we’ll give you surprisingly insightful recommendations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm">
            <h5>What are people reading?</h5>
            <p>There is no easy way to sort books, but here, you have the opportunity to discover top rated and liked books by users and read reviews about them.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<section class="recent-book-sec mt-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
            <h2>highly recommended books</h2>
            <hr>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            @foreach (var book in Model.RandomBooks)
            {
                <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-3 col-sm-4">
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="@book.PictureUrl" alt="Book Cover" style="height: 260px; width: 200px;">
                        <h3>
                            <a asp-controller="Books" 
                               asp-action="Details"
                               asp-route-id="@book.Id">
                                <em>@book.Title</em>
                            </a>
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            }
        </div>
        <div class="btn-sec">
            <a class="btn gray-btn"
               asp-controller="Books" 
               asp-action="TopRated">
            view top rated books
            </a>
            <a class="btn gray-btn"
               asp-controller="Books" 
               asp-action="NewReleases">
            view latest books
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="testimonial-sec">
    <div class="container">
        <div id="testimonal" class="owl-carousel owl-theme">
            <div class="item">
                <h3>Books are the quietest and most constant of friends; they are the most accessible and wisest of counselors, and the most patient of teachers.</h3>
                <div class="box-user">
                    <h4 class="author"><cite title="Source Title">Charles W. Eliot</cite></h4>
                    <span class="country"><cite title="Source Title">USA</cite></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>One glance at a book and you hear the voice of another person, perhaps someone dead for 1,000 years. To read is to voyage through time.</h3>
                <div class="box-user">
                    <h4 class="author">Carl Sagan</h4>
                    <span class="country">USA</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>Fairy tales are more than true: not because they tell us that dragons exist, but because they tell us that dragons can be beaten.</h3>
                <div class="box-user">
                    <h4 class="author">Neil Gaiman</h4>
                    <span class="country">Great Britain</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>I find television very educating. Every time somebody turns on the set, I go into the other room and read a book.</h3>
                <div class="box-user">
                    <h4 class="author">Groucho Marx</h4>
                    <span class="country">USA</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>In the case of good books, the point is not to see how many of them you can get through, but rather how many can get through to you.</h3>
                <div class="box-user">
                    <h4 class="author">Mortimer J. Adler</h4>
                    <span class="country">USA</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>Reading makes immigrants of us all. It takes us away from home, but more important, it finds homes for us everywhere.</h3>
                <div class="box-user">
                    <h4 class="author">Jean Rhys</h4>
                    <span class="country">Great Britain</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>So many books, so little time.</h3>
                <div class="box-user">
                    <h4 class="author">Frank Zappa</h4>
                    <span class="country">USA</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="left-quote">
        <img src="/images/left-quote.png" alt="quote">
    </div>
    <div class="right-quote">
        <img src="/images/right-quote.png" alt="quote">
    </div>
</section>
